{"tid":1462464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有comment話塞機場會令外國旅客對示威者有負面觀感","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:14.000Z","uid":175699,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b80146f3398876ee7afdbeb39467bf1e4c4f9760","tid":1462464,"uid":175699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"咁又點撚樣呀？你阻到侵侵定教宗呀？唔好傻啦，外國旅客有幾大影響力呀？你諗下如果你去到英國有脫歐示威者阻住你返香港，咁你返到香港做到啲咩呀？<br />\n<br />\n塞港鐵就ok，塞機場就屌撚哂鬼。屌你老母你同啲外國旅客有親呀？諗下場運動咁耐以嚟外國有冇幫過香港呀？一見到鬼佬就追住一地條撚去含<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d8d457ae3899c89cf5f80377e7e71f799fd5ce","tid":1462464,"uid":197149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"外國無用的話，我地之前眾籌登報係為咩？"},{"pid":"c6bcf877e4355bd1a82fecf76e3695ac59d8e37b","tid":1462464,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:39:32.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n建議集中火力搵出影響力最大嘅時間<br />\n睇下邊段時間最多人能響應，找出平衡<br />\n用隔日形式塞爆<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以最大化個運動成效</span></span></strong><br />\n隔日嘅好處係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">避免大家過勞和積累</span></strong>過多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">外國民怨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地團結一致</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"f3664d41421e61133f3efcb77f89832cf58f6349","tid":1462464,"uid":92989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b80146f3398876ee7afdbeb39467bf1e4c4f9760","tid":1462464,"uid":175699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"咁又點撚樣呀？你阻到侵侵定教宗呀？唔好傻啦，外國旅客有幾大影響力呀？你諗下如果你去到英國有脫歐示威者阻住你返香港，咁你返到香港做到啲咩呀？<br />\n<br />\n塞港鐵就ok，塞機場就屌撚哂鬼。屌你老母你同啲外國旅客有親呀？諗下場運動咁耐以嚟外國有冇幫過香港呀？一見到鬼佬就追住一地條撚去含<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"不合作運動可以，你可以坐，用人黎霸，但吾撚係拉住人 特登整d雜物塞住條路囉"},{"pid":"2a11958103e4d4bed54ddcda3ee0a70f70960b59","tid":1462464,"uid":92989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58d8d457ae3899c89cf5f80377e7e71f799fd5ce","tid":1462464,"uid":197149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"外國無用的話，我地之前眾籌登報係為咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"64d7050492e8d4d3e8140a6f014329a5c6baaa3e","tid":1462464,"uid":223075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"影響緊世界各地人對你地嘅睇法<br />\n係機場就做番個有禮貌嘅示威者"}]}